val testData = test.select("price", "bedrooms", "bathrooms", "sqft_living", "sqft_lot", "floors", "zipcode").map(sale => LabeledPoint(sale.getInt(0).toDouble, Vectors.dense(
    sale.getInt(1).toDouble, sale.getDouble(2), sale.getInt(3).toDouble, sale.getInt(4).toDouble, sale.getDouble(5), sale.getInt(6).toDouble)))
    
val trainingData = training.select("price", "bedrooms", "bathrooms", "sqft_living", "sqft_lot", "floors", "zipcode").map(sale => LabeledPoint(sale.getInt(0).toDouble, Vectors.dense(
    sale.getInt(1).toDouble, sale.getDouble(2), sale.getInt(3).toDouble, sale.getInt(4).toDouble, sale.getDouble(5), sale.getInt(6).toDouble)))

val numIterations = 100
val model = LinearRegressionWithSGD.train(trainingData, numIterations)

model.weights

val valuesAndPreds = testData.map { point =>
  val prediction = model.predict(point.features)
  (point.label, prediction)
}

val MSE = valuesAndPreds.map{case(v, p) => math.pow((v - p), 2)}.mean()
println("training Mean Squared Error = " + MSE)
